<h1 class="article header">Create an article about a new building</h1>
<p><a class='activate_modal' name='instructions' href='#'>For instructions on how to use markdown features click here</a></p>

<div id='mask' class='close_modal'></div>

<div id='instructions' class='modal_window'>
  <p>Formatting Instructions:</p>
  <p>*word* renders <i>word</i></p>
  <p>**word** renders <b>word</b></p>
  <p>#WARNINGS is written as such to make it a header</p>
  <p>##How to get into building is written as such to make it a secondary header</p>
  <p>Make sure to format apartment numbers in the same</p>
  <p>##Header format.</p>
</div>
<div class="article form new">
  <form class ="new-article-input" action="/articles/new" method="POST">
    <input type="text" name="header" placeholder="Address">
    <textarea rows="10" cols="40" type="text" name="body_text">
#WARNINGS

insert here

##How to get into building

insert here

##Format apartment numbers like this

insert relevant information about the apartment here
    </textarea>
    <input type="submit">
  </form>
</div>